sontalek - need high dps, around 100k, just a race to see who dies first.<br>
<br>
yelinak - mana drain suxor, normally just lose due to lack of mana on clerics, otherwise pretty easy, but long fight.<br>
<br>
----<br>
harder<br>
klandicar - unresistable ae, if slow doesnt stick early it gets interesting. not alot of hp though.<br>
<br>
keeper - unresistable ae, but indoors. hardest part is killing clearing around him without gating/warping.<br>
<br>
tormax - takes a while to get the pull down, straight melee fight. 7/8 day spawn with the best loot out of this group, hard to find up long.<br>
<br>
----<br>
weakest<br>
zlandicar - ae resistable, not alot of hp.<br>
<br>
statue - straight melee, spam healed till slowed and pretty easy. u get one thats resistant every once an a while like klandicar, fun fun.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
klandicar and zlandicar are 3 day spawns, sont too but hes a pain to mess with. if you get a good turn out for one of the other dragons, give sont a whirl while you're all together.<br>
<br>
