<br>
Klandicar is a pain since the ae dispells and is not resistable, but can be slowed easier than Zlandicar. Doesn't have a proc, but seems to have a stronger fear than Zlandicar. Just make sure you get him with a single pull as addds can mess you up. Also from time to time his death seems to summon glati and other cov mobs to his death spot. Kinda strange since it doesn't always happen.<br>
<br>
Statue is easier than Klandicar once slowed, but sometimes this bish likes to resist alot making it painful.<br>
<br>
KT<br>
<br>
Lendi<br>
<br>
Sontalak/Yelinak<br>
<br>
If you have mana burn wizards then Sontalak would be easier. If you have DB wizards without MB then Yelinak is easier.<br>
